The,Visa,Point,of,Sale,POS,Solutions,Program,gives,participating,payment,technology,providers,access,to,Visa,s,financial,transaction,network,Through,this,API,users,can,code,their,POS,systems,to,process,credit,payment,transactions,for,Visa,and,supported,cards,such,as,Discover,and,American,Express,Visa,will,also,provide,a,transaction,history,document,The,API,uses,XML,format,Public,documentation,is,not,available,and,developers,must,register,for,access